      • getAgentName

        java.lang.String getAgentName()
        Will return a name to identify the kind of agent that will be generated by this factory. This is useful for enabling the LearningAlgorithmExperimenter class to label the results for different kinds of agents that are tested.
        Returns:
        a name to identify the kind of agent that will be generated
